passives.name: Reap
passives.description: Killing a minion grants an additional 1 Gold, up to a maximum of 100 Gold. After having killed 100 minions, grants an additional 350 Gold and permanently disables this passive.

passives.name: Glory
passives.description: Gain 2 stacks for each champion kill and 1 stack for each assist, up to a maximum of 10 stacks. For every stack, gain 4 ability power, up to 40 at maximum stacks. Lose 5 stacks on death.

passives.name: Restoration
passives.description: Restore 1.25 mana every second. If you cannot gain mana, heal 0.55 health instead. Basic attacks deal 5 bonus physical damage on-hit against minions.

passives.name: Enduring Focus
